'''麥可·安德魯·雅澤姆斯基'''（{{lang-en|Michael Andrew Yastrzemski}}，{{bd|1990年|8月23日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手，目前效力於舊金山巨人。[[2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，金鶯隊在第14輪將他選走。他於2019年升上大聯盟，其祖父為紅襪隊傳奇名人堂球星[[卡爾·雅澤姆斯基|卡爾·雅澤姆斯基]]。
==職業生涯==
===舊金山巨人===
2019年5月25日，29歲的雅澤姆斯基終於升上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://boston.cbslocal.com/2019/05/26/mike-yastrzemski-carl-grandson-mlb-debut-giants|title=Carl Yastrzemski's Grandson Mike Makes Major League Debut|date=2019-05-26|publisher=[[WBZ-TV|WBZ-TV]]|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|access-date=2019-05-29}}</ref>他在隔天擊出大聯盟首安，不過卻被牽制出局。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=401075511|title=Marte homers, Diamondbacks sweep Giants|date=2019-05-26|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|access-date=2019-05-29}}</ref>5月31日，他敲出大聯盟首轟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/mike-yastrzemski-big-hits-vs-orioles|title=Yaz's grandson hits first HR against former team|date=2019-06-01|last=Guardado|first=Maria |work=MLB.com|access-date=2019-07-30}}</ref>8月16日，他更是達成單場三響砲的成就，還包含一發再見全壘打。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcsports.com/bayarea/giants/watch-giants-rookie-mike-yastrzemski-hit-three-homers-vs-diamondbacks|title=Watch Giants rookie Mike Yastrzemski hit three homers vs. Diamondbacks|first=Alex|last=Didion|publisher=[[NBC_Sports_Bay_Area|NBC Sports Bay Area]]|date=2019-08-16|access-date=2019-08-17}}</ref> 9月17日，他敲出了單季20轟，而且還是在他祖父以前效力的紅襪隊主場所擊出。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bleacherreport.com/articles/2854196-video-red-sox-legend-carl-yastrzemskis-grandson-mike-homers-at-fenway-park |title=Video: Red Sox Legend Carl Yastrzemski's Grandson Mike Homers at Fenway Park | Bleacher Report | Latest News, Videos and Highlights |publisher=Bleacher Report |date=2019-09-18 |access-date=2019-11-14}}</ref>該年他的打擊率為2成72，並敲出21轟與55分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/y/yastrmi01.shtml |title=Mike Yastrzemski Stats |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |access-date=2019-11-14}}</ref>他也是隊史繼1972年的[[戴夫·金曼|戴夫·金曼]]後，首位在菜鳥年便敲出20轟以上的球員。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eagletribune.com/sports/local_sports/sportsman-of-the-year-mike-yastrzemski-great-numbers-even-greater-perseverance/article_9d248eda-4d8d-54e6-ab94-97db2bb0c8e7.html|title=Sportsman of the Year: Mike Yastrzemski Great numbers, even greater perseverance|first=Bill Burt|last=bburt@eagletribune.com|website=Eagle-Tribune}}</ref>

2020年9月9日，他在第151場出賽敲出了生涯30轟。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/giants-into-top-nl-wild-card-spot-with-mariners-win|title=Anderson pushes Giants to top NL WC spot|website=MLB.com}}</ref>該年他的打擊率為2成97，並敲出10轟與35分打點。這年他也獲選為年度第二隊陣容。

==個人生活==
雅澤姆斯基的父親小卡爾<ref name=nytimes>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/12/sports/baseball/a-younger-yastrzemski-makes-his-way-at-vanderbilt.html|title=In the Name of a Legacy|date=2013-05-11|first=Tyler|last=Kepner|publisher=The New York Times|work=nytimes.com|access-date=2015-02-19}}</ref>曾在大學時期打過棒球，<ref name=boston>{{cite web|url=http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/articles/2009/02/04/the_yaz_family_craft/ |title=Boston Red Sox – Red Sox legend Carl Yastrzemski boosts grandson's budding baseball career|date=2009-02-04|last=Grossfeld|first=Stan|location=North Andover MA|publisher=The Boston Globe|work=boston.com|access-date=2014-07-30}}</ref>並於1984年至1988年間於小聯盟球隊效力，不過他並未升上大聯盟。<ref name="tennessee">{{cite web|url=http://www.tennessean.com/story/sports/college/vanderbilt/2014/07/23/mike-yastrzemski-vanderbilt-baseball-orioles-minor-leagues/13040217|title=Ex-Vanderbilt star Mike Yastrzemski tears up minors|date=2014-07-23|last=Driver|first=David|publisher=[[The_Tennessean|The Tennessean]]|work=tennessean.com|access-date=2014-07-30}}</ref>雅澤姆斯基在6歲時父母離異，<ref name=nytimes/>且父親在43歲時因為在動臀部手術時發生血栓去世。<ref name="bbyaz2min">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=yastrz002car|title=Mike Yastrzemski Minor Leagues Statistics and History|date=2019|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|access-date=2019-07-30}}</ref><ref name="findagraveyaz2">{{cite web|url=https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/62546236|title=Carl Michael Yastrzemski, Jr 1961–2004|date=2019|publisher=Finda A Grave|work=[[findagrave.com|findagrave.com]]|access-date=2019-07-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/31931624/exgibbons_standout_m_yastrzemski_dies|title=Ex-Gibbons standout M. Yastrzemski dies|newspaper=[[Sun-Sentinel|South Florida Sun-Sentinel]]|location=[[Fort_Lauderdale,_Florida|Fort Lauderdale, Florida]]|page=2D|date=2004-09-20|access-date=2019-05-25|via=newspapers.com}}</ref>於是雅澤姆斯基長大後由其祖父卡爾教他打棒球。<ref name=boston/><ref name="boston_draft">{{cite web|url=http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/extras/extra_bases/2009/06/sox_draft_micha.html|title=Sox draft Michael Yastrzemski – Extra Bases – Red Sox blog|date=2009-06-11|last=Finn|first=Chad|publisher=The Boston Globe|work=boston.com|access-date=2014-07-30}}</ref><ref name=boston2>{{cite web|url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/sports/2014/03/02/carl-yastrzemski-hand-see-grandson-play/THV5ASAyRQWt0yxChi0jPJ/story.html?s_campaign=sm_tw|title=Carl Yastrzemski on hand to see grandson play – Sports|date=2014-03-02|last=Cafardo|first=Nick|location=Ft Myers FL|publisher=The Boston Globe|work=bostonglobe.com|access-date=2014-07-30}}</ref>而他在2018年結婚。
